<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Nevertheless...</font>

76
00:08:04,580 --> 00:08:05,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55" color="#d6d6d6">Nevertheless...</font>

77
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:08,140
