78
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:11,900
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Damn!</font>

79
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:13,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What a tricky guy!</font>

80
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:18,690
<font face="Impress BT" size="38"><i>Omomi: Weight</i></font>

81
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>We're being crushed!</i></font>

82
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,900
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're so cool, General!</font>

83
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,870
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">How is that cool?!</font>

84
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:30,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What is this?</font>

85
00:08:30,490 --> 00:08:32,820
