88
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:48,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Be careful of gusts.</font>

89
00:08:59,730 --> 00:09:01,360
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Do you understand now?</font>

90
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:05,290
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is the weather science of Weatheria.</font>

91
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:14,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Don't underestimate it!</font>

92
00:09:20,270 --> 00:09:22,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Eh?  Huh?</font>

93
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:23,860
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Where'd Chopper go?</font>

94
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:26,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Get him!</font>

95
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:30,120
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Damn it... I was thrown out of the tank.</font>

96
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Guess I've got no choice but to fight.</font>

97
00:09:36,110 --> 00:09:37,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">But there's no reason to fear!</font>

98
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:41,130
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm not the same weakling that I used to be!</font>

99
00:09:52,130 --> 00:09:53,520
<font face="Impress BT" size="38"><i>Bamboo Javelin-Grove</i></font>

100
00:09:57,690 --> 00:10:00,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Heracles'n-sensei!</font>

101
00:10:00,780 --> 00:10:03,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I spent two years in that forest, fighting for my life.</font>

102
00:10:03,180 --> 00:10:04,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I couldn't drop my guard for a second!</font>

103
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:06,440
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I won't forget that!</font>

104
00:10:07,110 --> 00:10:09,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Now it begins!</i></font>

105
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:16,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>The second chapter of Usopp the Man's Adventure!</i></font>

106
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:23,320
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'll rig the entire plaza with pitfalls!</font>

107
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:25,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They can bring robots or whatever they want.</font>

108
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:28,620
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">When they're trapped in a hole, it's all over for them!</font>

109
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,020
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?</font>

110
00:10:33,260 --> 00:10:35,640
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I can hear someone else digging through the earth...</font>

111
00:10:53,680 --> 00:10:56,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Daruma-san went flying!</font>

112
00:10:58,590 --> 00:11:00,250
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">W-Who are you?!</font>

113
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:03,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's me!</font>

114
00:11:14,450 --> 00:11:17,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm good at digging through the earth too!</font>

115
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:18,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Chopper!</font>

116
00:11:19,810 --> 00:11:24,600
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Awesome!  You've learned how to turn into a stag beetle?!</font>

117
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,130
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>I'm not a beetle!</i></font>

118
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:32,330
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I improved my transformation points over the past two years.</font>

119
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:37,120
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Now only one of my transformations needs a Rumble Ball.</font>

120
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:41,700
