121
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:44,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You cheeky coral bastard!</font>

122
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:46,020
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'll tear you to shreds!</font>

123
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,730
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This isn't coral, they're horns!</font>

124
00:11:49,110 --> 00:11:50,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">And I...</font>

125
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:53,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">am a cheeky <i>monster!</i></font>

126
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:00,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">How many did you kill?</font>

127
00:12:02,210 --> 00:12:04,270
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Z-Zero...</font>

128
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:12,320
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Kraken!</font>

129
00:12:13,410 --> 00:12:15,710
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Well done, I didn't think you had it in you.</font>

130
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:20,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They believed you and you captured Shirahoshi.</font>

131
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:25,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Now crush her!</font>

132
00:12:30,260 --> 00:12:33,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Your brothers still live in the North Pole.</font>

