00:12:34,050 --> 00:12:36,650
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I know exactly where they are.</font>

134
00:12:37,220 --> 00:12:41,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We could kill them any time we like.</font>

135
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:45,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You are legendary creatures...</font>

