<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Surume!</font>

143
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:52,500
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You became his slave... to protect your siblings?</font>

144
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:58,620
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I see, of course you want to protect them.</font>

145
00:13:58,620 --> 00:14:02,070
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Are they your younger siblings?  Or older?</font>

146
00:14:04,230 --> 00:14:06,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Let me protect them too!</font>

147
00:14:15,910 --> 00:14:17,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Here comes Straw Hat!</font>

148
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:20,250
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Kill him!</font>

