158
00:15:05,390 --> 00:15:06,290
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?!</font>

159
00:15:16,930 --> 00:15:21,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Now I'm really fired up!</i></font>

160
00:15:44,010 --> 00:15:45,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh no!</font>

