<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat!</font>

177
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:15,850
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He sure is tough.</font>

178
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:19,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Do you have any idea what Fishman Karate can do?!</font>

