<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He took his head right off!</font>

180
00:17:21,490 --> 00:17:23,390
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Alright!  And it only took one hit!</font>

181
00:17:26,370 --> 00:17:28,010
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That won't work on me...</font>

182
00:17:28,010 --> 00:17:29,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">'cause I'm rubber!</font>

183
00:17:29,430 --> 00:17:33,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Compared to Jinbe's attacks, that didn't even itch!</font>

184
00:17:33,470 --> 00:17:37,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's right!  It's because you rely on fake power!</font>

185
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="38"><i>Head Armament</i></font>

186
00:17:41,980 --> 00:17:44,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Steel Shell Squadron!</font>

187
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:48,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You fool!  Your head's gonna shatter!</font>

188
00:17:54,570 --> 00:17:55,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="38"><i>Bell</i></font>

189
00:17:59,990 --> 00:18:02,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Steel lost to his head!</i></font>

190
00:18:48,620 --> 00:18:50,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">None of them are hitting?!</font>

191
00:18:50,380 --> 00:18:52,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Does he know where every single one is going?!</font>

192
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:54,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're amazing, Luffy-sama!</font>

193
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:56,920
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's the Haki of Perception!</font>

194
00:19:22,950 --> 00:19:25,290
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Captain Hody!</i></font>

195
00:19:39,090 --> 00:19:42,670
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Luffy-sama... How strong <i>are</i> you?</font>

196
00:19:43,300 --> 00:19:46,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat Luffy is amazing!</font>

197
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:50,850
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So this is the power of a world-famous pirate?</font>

198
00:19:56,730 --> 00:19:58,330
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Whaaat?!</font>

199
00:19:58,330 --> 00:20:00,620
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">T-That's...</font>

200
00:20:00,620 --> 00:20:04,670
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">the Noah, from the Fishman District!</font>

201
00:20:04,670 --> 00:20:08,230
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Why is the Noah above Fishman Island?!</font>

202
00:20:08,230 --> 00:20:11,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's clearly falling toward the plaza!</font>

203
00:20:11,590 --> 00:20:14,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's going to break the bubble around the island!</font>

204
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:17,620
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Fishman Island will be destroyed without the bubble!</font>

205
00:20:17,620 --> 00:20:18,940
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We'll all be washed away!</font>

206
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:23,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What's that?!</font>

207
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:24,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Noah?!</font>

208
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:30,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's super-huge!</font>

209
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:34,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">If that ship hits us, the entire island will be crushed!</font>

210
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:37,220
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Who's steering it?!</font>

211
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:40,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">No, the Noah shouldn't even have the power to move!</font>

212
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:43,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What is that?!</font>

213
00:20:43,450 --> 00:20:44,400
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's huge!</font>

214
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:47,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I don't know what's happening, but we're doomed!</font>

215
00:20:47,970 --> 00:20:50,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I wonder, if we're all crushed at the same time...</font>

216
00:20:50,430 --> 00:20:52,550
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">will the ocean become red?</font>

217
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:55,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Don't jinx us by saying such horrible things!</font>

218
00:20:55,430 --> 00:20:57,490
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Evacuate!</font>

219
00:20:57,490 --> 00:20:59,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Flee to the waters outside the island!</font>

220
00:21:14,530 --> 00:21:17,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">E-Everyone...</font>

221
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:20,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What is that?</font>

222
00:21:36,810 --> 00:21:41,140
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Owie... I slipped.</font>

223
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:44,810
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're... Decken's subordinate, Wadatsumi!</font>

224
00:21:48,860 --> 00:21:52,260
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Cap'n Vander Decken!</font>

225
00:21:52,260 --> 00:21:55,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I fell off!</font>

226
00:21:55,190 --> 00:21:58,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Pwease stop da ship!</font>

227
00:21:58,410 --> 00:22:00,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I don' wanna die!</font>

228
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:04,710
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Decken?!  What is going on?!</font>

229
00:22:05,790 --> 00:22:07,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Captain Hody!</font>

230
00:22:07,790 --> 00:22:09,850
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Are you alright?!</font>

231
00:22:09,850 --> 00:22:13,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Uh, is this... part of the plan?!</font>

232
00:22:13,340 --> 00:22:17,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It looks like Decken is moving that ship!</font>

233
00:22:19,550 --> 00:22:22,270
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Be quiet, you useless worms!</font>

234
00:22:22,700 --> 00:22:25,270
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Damn Straw Hat...</font>

235
00:22:25,270 --> 00:22:29,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Huh?  How is he still standing?</font>

236
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:31,070
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I even attacked him using the Color of Arms.</font>

237
00:22:37,740 --> 00:22:41,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Decken, is it?  That insane pirate!</font>

238
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:44,710
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This wasn't part of the plan!</font>

239
00:23:01,290 --> 00:23:04,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Shirahoshi!</font>

240
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:07,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Accept... my love!</font>

241
00:23:17,600 --> 00:23:21,440
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Cap'n Decken!  What 'bout me?!</font>

242
00:23:23,590 --> 00:23:25,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Wadatsumi?</font>

243
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:29,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's no longer possible to save you!</font>

244
00:23:29,420 --> 00:23:35,270
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You will become a sacrifice for the death
of Shirahoshi, just like the rest of Fishman Island!</font>

245
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:36,330
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">No way!</font>

246
00:23:40,250 --> 00:23:44,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We're done for!  The bubble won't hold!</font>

247
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:46,210
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is the end!</font>

248
00:23:46,210 --> 00:23:49,580
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hey, where'd Princess Shirahoshi go?</font>

249
00:23:49,580 --> 00:23:50,930
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">She's gone!</font>

250
00:23:51,550 --> 00:23:55,880
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?  The Princess!  Princess Shirahoshi!</font>

251
00:23:57,930 --> 00:24:01,440
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?  Shirahoshi disappeared?!</font>

252
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:03,520
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I-Impossible!</font>

253
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:06,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm up here!</font>

254
00:24:09,410 --> 00:24:10,850
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Princess Shirahoshi!</font>

255
00:24:10,850 --> 00:24:11,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">When did she...</font>

256
00:24:11,890 --> 00:24:13,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Mermaid Princess?!</font>

257
00:24:13,830 --> 00:24:16,990
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Shirahoshi!  What is she doing up there?!</font>

258
00:24:16,990 --> 00:24:21,280
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Basically, that ship is flying at Shirahoshi!</font>

259
00:24:22,370 --> 00:24:24,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The woman I love!</font>

260
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:30,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">M-My life is your target, is it not?!</font>

261
00:24:30,780 --> 00:24:34,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">If you just want to take my life...</font>

262
00:24:34,510 --> 00:24:38,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">then the people of Ryuuguu Kingdom should not be caught up in it.</font>

263
00:24:38,760 --> 00:24:40,710
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Please, leave them alone!</font>

264
00:24:42,930 --> 00:24:45,000
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I am right here!</font>

265
00:24:45,420 --> 00:24:49,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Princess!  Shirahoshi-sama!</i></font>

266
00:24:50,060 --> 00:24:54,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So basically, that insane Decken-guy...</font>

267
00:24:55,110 --> 00:24:59,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">was planning to crush the whole island, and us with it.</font>

268
00:25:01,550 --> 00:25:04,120
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He betrayed me!</font>

269
00:25:07,410 --> 00:25:10,880
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Ah, she's going to sacrifice herself for us!</font>

270
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:13,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Isn't there anything we can do to help her?</font>

271
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:21,570
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh, how...</font>

272
00:25:22,350 --> 00:25:27,110
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh, how completely beautiful you are, Shirahoshi!  Even your heart shines with it!</font>

273
00:25:27,120 --> 00:25:33,130
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're trying to avert this disaster
and save your country all by yourself, Shirahoshi?</font>

274
00:25:36,290 --> 00:25:38,860
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Shirahoshi!</font>

275
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:46,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Shira... hoshi.</font>

276
00:25:46,590 --> 00:25:52,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You truly are
worthy of becoming Vander Decken the Ninth's wife!</font>

277
00:25:55,220 --> 00:26:00,980
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Die at the height of your beauty, and live on forever in my heart!</font>

278
00:26:00,980 --> 00:26:03,070
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Shirahoshi!</font>

279
00:26:05,390 --> 00:26:07,060
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Your Highness!</font>

280
00:26:15,220 --> 00:26:19,430
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That Weak-hoshi...
Even after I told her to stay close to me!</font>

281
00:26:20,780 --> 00:26:22,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat is...</font>

282
00:26:22,190 --> 00:26:24,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Captain Hody!</font>

283
00:26:24,190 --> 00:26:27,070
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">H-Huh?  Hody-san isn't here!</font>

284
00:26:28,510 --> 00:26:30,720
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Look up in the sky!  There he is!</font>

285
00:26:31,810 --> 00:26:33,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Under Noah?!</font>

286
00:26:47,610 --> 00:26:50,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're completely insane, Vander Decken.</font>

287
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:53,550
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">However, this is a great trump card!</font>

288
00:27:14,990 --> 00:27:19,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That bastard... How dare he harm Shirahoshi-chan?!</font>

289
00:27:19,380 --> 00:27:21,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Sanji, wait!</font>

290
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:25,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'll jump up there!  You take care of the plaza!</font>

291
00:27:25,090 --> 00:27:26,590
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Got it!</font>

292
00:27:27,210 --> 00:27:30,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">But anyway Luffy, the ship is underwater!</font>

293
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:33,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Do you think there's water inside the ship too, Jinbe?</font>

294
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:38,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm not sure, but Decken is a Devil Fruit user...</font>

295
00:27:38,410 --> 00:27:42,210
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">so we can assume that there must be air in there somewhere since he can make the ship move.</font>

296
00:27:42,210 --> 00:27:44,020
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">If you're going to go, take this.</font>

297
00:27:45,040 --> 00:27:47,150
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's a coral that creates a bubble.</font>

298
00:27:47,750 --> 00:27:48,860
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Okay!</font>

299
00:27:54,650 --> 00:27:58,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Okay, I leave my beloved Shirahoshi-chan to you!</font>

300
00:27:58,480 --> 00:28:00,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm gonna fling you, Luffy!</font>

301
00:28:03,830 --> 00:28:04,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Do it!</font>

